=================================   Installation and Configure   =========================================================

1. Git pull files
2. Import Database from /Inside4/DataBaseModel/ikiev_inside4.sql
3. Rename config_default.php to config.php and fill all variables
4. Make folder "Uploads" in the root folder

5. Register a user who will be an admin
6. Insert user_id of this user and group_id = 1 in auth_users_groups table
7. Try Inside Admin Panel by the Admin User

=================================   Mobile Apps   =======================================================================

You can put /MobileApp code into Cordova project
In the /MobileApp/cordova folder you can find more info for this process

